    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Medieval Builders: Strongholds &amp; Castles.</strong> Your kingdom is waiting for you!</h2><strong>Live a medieval life full of wars and legends. Craft, build and defend kingdoms. Solve your subjects' problems to increase their population.</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/42ee57a2eec108e82414db0e3e9638a9.poster.avif?t=1726481461\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/42ee57a2eec108e82414db0e3e9638a9.webm?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/42ee57a2eec108e82414db0e3e9638a9.mp4?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>Became a king of the no man's land or conquer other strongholds. Do it by yourself or with friends and start a dynasty</strong><br><br>Became a medieval builder of villages, towns and castles. Trade with merchants or craft equipment and decoration yourself.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/0dd020678770db96fe9108f39e0c856f.poster.avif?t=1726481461\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/0dd020678770db96fe9108f39e0c856f.webm?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/0dd020678770db96fe9108f39e0c856f.mp4?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Take care of and breed animals on a farm....<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/2aa255218d6a5b6d935fdaa486a525c4.poster.avif?t=1726481461\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/2aa255218d6a5b6d935fdaa486a525c4.webm?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/2aa255218d6a5b6d935fdaa486a525c4.mp4?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Or survive by hunting and harvesting!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/a796e2e820b95c667565048d0171bc03.poster.avif?t=1726481461\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/a796e2e820b95c667565048d0171bc03.webm?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/a796e2e820b95c667565048d0171bc03.mp4?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Decorate the medieval interiors.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/079834c590e204cee67d895ebf6d3151.poster.avif?t=1726481461\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/079834c590e204cee67d895ebf6d3151.webm?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2175890/extras/079834c590e204cee67d895ebf6d3151.mp4?t=1726481461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
